317
00:18:50.156 --> 00:18:53.976
Importantly, a subset of these tumors undergo clonal

318
00:18:53.996 --> 00:18:57.816
plasticity and transition into neuroendocrine prostate

319
00:18:57.876 --> 00:18:59.576
cancer, or called NEPC.

320
00:19:00.756 --> 00:19:04.276
This highly aggressive subtype is characterized by

321
00:19:04.496 --> 00:19:08.376
