669
00:39:55.644 --> 00:39:58.464
And then if we look at the solo WCDW sites,

670
00:39:59.424 --> 00:40:03.364
which are known to lose methylation as a function of replication, what you can

671
00:40:03.404 --> 00:40:07.304
