674
00:40:16.724 --> 00:40:17.844
but losses are not.

675
00:40:19.164 --> 00:40:22.264
Then if we look at in vivo tCGI data

676
00:40:23.264 --> 00:40:27.184
from colon cancer, what we observe is while the colon

677
00:40:27.244 --> 00:40:30.944
cancer starts at a higher point, it gains

678
00:40:31.064 --> 00:40:34.184
methylation at a trajectory that's very similar to the healthy.

679
00:40:35.204 --> 00:40:39.064
Then if we look at solo WCDW sites, what we

680
00:40:39.104 --> 00:40:42.964
