The natural product and macrocyclic screens were done in

1223
01:12:19.288 --> 01:12:23.108
collaboration with the University of Michigan Center for Chemical Genomics.

1224
01:12:23.868 --> 01:12:27.628
I thank my IDT team, support from the Postdoctoral Affairs Office of

1225
01:12:27.648 --> 01:12:31.468
